{"tid":2265043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大J推出街頭服裝品牌《boyhood.》 嗰女model幾gfable","createTime":"2020-10-31T06:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T09:31:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f39c668619c23f902f0354096e077825ae291910","tid":2265043,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ue4qwXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUe4qwXT.png&h=bca77080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚成晚都訓唔著，因爲好緊張。<br />\n我籌備左好多個月既街頭服裝品牌《boyhood.》正式開業。<br />\n▼馬上瀏覽boyhood.網店!▼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.boyhood.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyhood.jp%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0UsakxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=24950f3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.boyhood.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然剛剛係YouTube都有出條片簡單解釋過點解想搞個品牌，不過係呢度都想文字講一次。<br />\n<br />\n1，觀衆donation/付費會員<br />\n一路以來我都好開心，有好多觀衆選擇用付費形式去訂閲我既youtube頻道，係我遊戲直播既時候，久不久又會有觀衆donate表示支持。<br />\n不過我一路都有個心結，就係我無任何實體既野去俾返大家<br />\n通過搞呢個品牌，好支持既觀衆就可以有野收到手上<br />\n<br />\n2，我著衫好老夫子<br />\n我平時自己買衫，著得舒服既衫我會買好多件，一樣cutting一樣size，唔同print唔同色...etc.<br />\n可惜經常想買第2件既時候，好多時件產品已經下架，想買都買唔到...<br />\n我自己生產，自己品牌，以後我想要咩衫褲，我一定可以買到。<br />\n<br />\n3，正所謂槍打出頭鳥，自舊年6月起，我接到既宣傳工作已經越來越少，終於係呢個10月份，我地正式收皮了~ 0宣傳工作offer。哈哈哈哈...<br />\n無品牌揾我宣傳咩？無問題，我自己搞一個！<br />\n<br />\n基本上就係咁喇。<br />\n<br />\n關於更多產品既資料，大家可以去網店睇睇，或者係youtube/facebook留言問，我答到就盡量答。<br />\n<br />\n等陣食完lunch我會開始直播打機，大家亦可以去我直播度發問。<br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁啦。<br />\n產品種類比較少。我初期投資好難搞太多種類，希望以後可以慢慢增加。"},{"pid":"7723a07a3c2a4efb99fe26d816700f46311c7d49","tid":2265043,"uid":344567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"俾返大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3186348c4a7c4e4ad03e5f07a6b4f567bef7ea","tid":2265043,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7723a07a3c2a4efb99fe26d816700f46311c7d49","tid":2265043,"uid":344567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"俾返大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:29:01.000Z","msg":"真心幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對眼識講嘢咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01jqwZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01jqwZd.png&h=039b3eca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"817ab86b7090f4a68211178cea20f87cfc3075b8","tid":2265043,"uid":187192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"正, 我地伍仔又可以繼續出片屌大j<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9604327f88c2c109fa3aba5a54c5c2554b68a945","tid":2265043,"uid":295224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3186348c4a7c4e4ad03e5f07a6b4f567bef7ea","tid":2265043,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7723a07a3c2a4efb99fe26d816700f46311c7d49","tid":2265043,"uid":344567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"俾返大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:29:01.000Z","msg":"真心幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對眼識講嘢咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01jqwZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01jqwZd.png&h=039b3eca&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"女 邊個黍?"},{"pid":"63e2c21f5fd854bfa2875ff4c37d304a5a8fc9b8","tid":2265043,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9604327f88